Script "Input Limit" name="Input Limit"
Browser find tagname=div text="Add Credits" elaction=click timeout=30s
Wait 1s
Mouse click to=x:682,y:339
Press Ctrl+A
Press BACKSPACE
Type 99999999999999999999999
Browser find class="text-4xl font-extrabold font-cairo px-1" tagname=span text=$99,990.00 elaction=click timeout=30s style="margin-top: -25px;"
Click image template=wc38.png
Script "Input Limit" action=end name="Input Limit"
